      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<title>Bloc 4: AI Solution Presentation</title>\n<style>\n  body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; margin: 0; background: #0f172a; color: white; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 100vh; overflow: hidden; }\n  .presentation-wrapper { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 100%; height: 100%; }\n  .slide-container { width: 900px; height: 500px; background: white; color: #334155; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); padding: 50px; position: relative; display: none; box-sizing: border-box; }\n  .slide-container.active { display: flex; flex-direction: column; animation: fadeIn 0.5s; }\n  @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }\n  .header { color: #0f172a; border-bottom: 3px solid #10b981; padding-bottom: 15px; margin-bottom: 25px; }\n  h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 2.2rem; }\n  h2 { color: #047857; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 0; }\n  ul { font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #475569; }\n  .controls { margin-top: 30px; display: flex; gap: 15px; z-index: 10; }\n  button { padding: 12px 24px; cursor: pointer; background: #10b981; color: white; border: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1rem; }\n  button:hover { background: #047857; }\n  button:disabled { background: #94a3b8; cursor: not-allowed; }\n  .slide-number { position: absolute; bottom: 20px; right: 30px; font-weight: bold; color: #94a3b8; }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<div class=\"presentation-wrapper\">\n  <div id=\"slides\">\n    <div class=\"slide-container active\">\n        <div class=\"header\"><h1>Aurora Tech: AI Solutions</h1></div>\n        <h2>End-to-End MLOps Defense Presentation</h2>\n        <ul>\n            <li><strong>Objective:</strong> Industrialize an AI margin prediction application.</li>\n            <li><strong>Module:</strong> Bloc 4 - AI Solutions & Visualization</li>\n            <li><strong>Duration:</strong> 15 minutes Defense</li>\n        </ul>\n        <div class=\"slide-number\">Slide 1 / 8</div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"slide-container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"><h1>1. Problem Statement</h1></div>\n        <h2>Margin volatility</h2>\n        <ul>\n            <li>Supply chain issues and volatile EUR/USD exchange rates threaten our 8% profit margin.</li>\n            <li>Goal: Predict extreme cost compressions proactively.</li>\n            <li>Data Source: <code>fact_chromebook_margin_risk</code> from Bloc 2 Warehouse.</li>\n        </ul>\n        <div class=\"slide-number\">Slide 2 / 8</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"slide-container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"><h1>2. The Machine Learning Model</h1></div>\n        <h2>Random Forest Classifier</h2>\n        <ul>\n            <li>Chosen for excellence in handling non-linear relationships (FX vs Shipping modes).</li>\n            <li>Features: EUR/USD, EUR/TWD, Delay Days, Freight Cost.</li>\n            <li>Label: Margin Impact Detected (0/1).</li>\n        </ul>\n        <div class=\"slide-number\">Slide 3 / 8</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"slide-container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"><h1>3. Serving Infrastructure</h1></div>\n        <h2>FastAPI Endpoint Integration</h2>\n        <ul>\n            <li>Model serialized using <code>joblib</code> resulting in a self-contained artifact.</li>\n            <li>FastAPI serves the artifact on a <code>/predict-margin-risk</code> REST endpoint.</li>\n            <li>Pydantic schemas ensure valid payload inputs.</li>\n        </ul>\n        <div class=\"slide-number\">Slide 4 / 8</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"slide-container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"><h1>4. Architecture & Containerization</h1></div>\n        <h2>MLOps Deployment Flow</h2>\n        <div style=\"display:flex; justify-content:center; align-items:center; gap:15px; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 0.9rem;\">\n            <div style=\"background:#f1f5f9; padding:10px; border-radius:6px; text-align:center; border:1px solid #cbd5e1; color: #334155;\"><b>Scikit-Learn</b><br/><small>train_model.py</small></div>\n            <div style=\"color:#10b981;\">&#10141; <small>.pkl</small> &#10141;</div>\n            <div style=\"background:#d1fae5; padding:10px; border-radius:6px; text-align:center; border:2px solid #10b981; color:#065f46;\"><b>FastAPI Server</b><br/><small>Port 8000</small></div>\n            <div style=\"color:#10b981;\">&#10141; <small>Wraps</small> &#10141;</div>\n            <div style=\"background:#0f172a; padding:10px; border-radius:6px; text-align:center; border:2px solid #3b82f6; color:white;\"><b>Docker Container</b><br/><small>Python 3.10 Slim</small></div>\n        </div>\n        <ul style=\"font-size: 1.1rem;\">\n            <li>Entire FastAPI application wrapped in a reproducible environment.</li>\n            <li>Eliminates \"It works on my machine\" ML dependency issues.</li>\n        </ul>\n        <div class=\"slide-number\">Slide 5 / 8</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"slide-container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"><h1>5. CI/CD Operations</h1></div>\n        <h2>Continuous Integration via GitHub Actions</h2>\n        <ul>\n            <li>Every commit merges triggers <code>mlops-ci.yml</code> workflow.</li>\n            <li>Automated PyTest gates ensure no broken models are pushed to production API.</li>\n        </ul>\n        <div class=\"slide-number\">Slide 6 / 8</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"slide-container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"><h1>6. Automated Retraining</h1></div>\n        <h2>Concept Drift Mitigation</h2>\n        <ul>\n            <li>System monitors macroeconomic drift on the EUR profile continuously.</li>\n            <li>If drift > 5% threshold detected, a Jenkins/Airflow trigger executes <code>train_model.py</code> on new warehouse data automatically.</li>\n        </ul>\n        <div class=\"slide-number\">Slide 7 / 8</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"slide-container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"><h1>Conclusion & Actionable Output</h1></div>\n        <h2>Tying back to business value</h2>\n        <ul>\n            <li>If risk probability > 85%, API yields an actionable Web3 alert for treasury managers.</li>\n            <li>Dashboard integrated to view these predictions live.</li>\n            <li><strong>Thank you. Ready for Q&A.</strong></li>\n        </ul>\n        <div class=\"slide-number\">Slide 8 / 8</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"controls\">\n    <button id=\"prevBtn\" onclick=\"prevSlide()\" disabled>Previous Slide</button>\n    <button id=\"nextBtn\" onclick=\"nextSlide()\">Next Slide</button>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<script>\n  let currentSlide = 0;\n  const slides = document.querySelectorAll('.slide-container');\n  const prevBtn = document.getElementById('prevBtn');\n  const nextBtn = document.getElementById('nextBtn');\n\n  function showSlide(index) {\n    slides.forEach(s => s.classList.remove('active'));\n    slides[index].classList.add('active');\n    prevBtn.disabled = index === 0;\n    nextBtn.disabled = index === slides.length - 1;\n  }\n  function nextSlide() { if (currentSlide < slides.length - 1) { currentSlide++; showSlide(currentSlide); } }\n  function prevSlide() { if (currentSlide > 0) { currentSlide--; showSlide(currentSlide); } }\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>\n",
